author: maxb
msg: SWIG: Implement a %hash_argout_typemap helper, and use it throughout to
reduce duplication of code in the bindings. However, leave conditionals in
place, so that this change produces no functional change in the generated
wrappers. I'll remove the conditionals in a future revision.
[in subversion/bindings/swig/]
* include/svn_containers.swg: Add %hash_argout_typemap definition and use it.
* svn_fs.i, svn_repos.i, svn_wc.i: Use it here too.

author: djh
msg: Fix generator to avoid build warnings and failures if serf is not used.

(get_install_targets): Drop serf from target list if we don't have it.
